QuestData.Title: Corruption Runs Deep
QuestData.Description: Today you learn that no one can be trusted in times of war, Wakener. Even those closest to the Klaxxi are susceptible to corruption.$b$bWho knows how long this traitor has been corrupted. He must be destroyed!$b$bYou appear confused. Do you not see the traitor in our midst? Allow me to adjust your vision.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat the traitor in the Duskroot Fen.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat the traitor in the Duskroot Fen
